api_list.name: Providers
api_list.description:
Get all available streaming providers.

Returns a list of all available streaming providers.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://test20186.p.rapidapi.com/watch/providers"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "test20186.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
